Well, about a month late...but it's fairly simple.  It'll be a while until you can truly solo the way Rangers are built to, as you don't get panic animal till late teens or early 20s IIRC...

The main method is SoW on yourself (if you can get it, you get it for yourself at level 30, IIRC), then snare your target.  Then fear it and drop some dots on it.  Then chase after it hacking away.  Don't use a bow...until you get into your upper 50s or 60s, the bow just doesn't do any damage worth mentioning.

Until you get fear, it's pretty much snare at a distance...drop your DoTs on it, then hack it when it gets to you.

